Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:08.65,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:15.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:22.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:30.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:34.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:37.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:45.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:52.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:57.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:04.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:08.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:11.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:15.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(367.167,140.389)}Hongo Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,700.389)}Becomes a Cactus Monster!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This arrived today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The sender isn't marked, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A package with no return address...\NIt's a bit unsettling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a cactus like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you study them for a living... how\Ncan there be a cactus you haven't seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stand, Doctor Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stand, and come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to turn you into Cactusbat,\Na cyborg fusion of cactus and bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems a fitting role for\Na man who dedicated his life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to the study of cacti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is already infused\Nwith cactus extract, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the alterations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Cactusbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Suzuki and Yasuoka of the Council\Nof Scientists For World Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking awfully pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming down with a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Chai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda... I didn't realize you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda... W-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Yasuoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:35.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Vice chairman of the Council of Scientists\NFor World Peace, Doctor Motoichiro Yasuoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,has gone missing after an attack\Nby an unidentified assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Strict security precautions\Nhave been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now for our next story...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,just my father, but Doctor Yasuoka too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You really believe the cactus you\Nfound on the scene was your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking out two major figures\Nfrom that peace council...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to have serious consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the plan was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've taken out those fools\Nwith their talk of "world peace."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking out those two will\Nhobble their organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no further need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, turn all the people\Nof Japan into cacti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate Operation: World\NCactus Transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Cactusbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bury Japan in cacti and\Nturn it into a desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who killed Doctor Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me... the Gel Shocker\Nmonster, Cactusbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And my hand will turn you\Ninto a cactus as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, help that man. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... I don't have\Ntime to fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I must execute Operation:\NWorld Cactus Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:11:00.72,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy out there gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. Giving cacti as presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. That's dangerous.\NGive it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The thorn won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Mr. Suzuki and have\Nhim come by right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairman's hand turned into a cactus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We got to him early, so the poison\Nwon't spread to his entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd never taken that cactus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suzuki... please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Create a vaccine as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom and dad got turned into cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get to safety!\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... we'll finish this another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you come back so soon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispose of that weakling monster at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Please wait a moment, my leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:14:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I analyzed the broken claw to\Ncalculate Rider's strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then modified its hand\Nto endure those values.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, even if Rider interferes,\Nhe'll destroy him without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the hand off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut my hand off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it to make a vaccine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First your father, and Doctor Yasuoka, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of all the\Npeople turned into cacti,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one hand seems like a minor sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need something for your research,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,use my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We need the vaccine quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, we'll\Nonly see more victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 2,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's lovely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It puts out red flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cactusbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue with your efforts\Nto turn people into cacti!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of him. \NKeep working on the vaccine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... can you really fight\Nwith your hand in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Can't make your vaccine now, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, I'll turn you all into cacti!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here and suffer until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, it's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand has recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you did it! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.\NYou take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry\N- Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a cactus yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:09.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:13.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:16.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:20.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:31.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:06.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.70,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.21,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Including Mr. Suzuki's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Yasuoka, and Kiyoshi's parents, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Suzuki's vaccine turned\Nthem all back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, we beat Cactusbat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cactusbat?\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of that cactus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are in the dark, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:02.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrifying Operation: World\NCactus Transformation was halted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:07.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when would Rider's hard fight\Nto achieve world peace end?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(275.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:16.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Geldam's insatiable ambitions lead\Nto Geldam's leader finally appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:21.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Geldam's science division works hard to\Ncreate a transformation stoppage system.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:25.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is frozen in his\Ntransformation pose at absolute zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:31.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Hongo\NTakeshi Cannot Transform!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:31.16,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fscy124\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,710.389)}Hongo Takeshi Cannot Transform!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:39.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:42.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:54.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:24:01.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:06.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:12.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi Becomes\Na Cactus Monster!?